                    <article>
                        <h3 class="article-title">How do I verify my account?</h3>
                        <div class="free-content excerpted"><p><b>Identification document</b> -  Driver's license, Photo ID, Firearm Owners ID (FOID), Tribal ID, U.S. Military ID, Passport or Passport Card is used to authenticate your identity. The stated document should show an identity picture, number, full name, date of birth, date of issue and expiry as well as governmental institutions. </p>
</div>
                        <div class="link-wrapper">
                            <a data-analytics="buttonClick" href="/support/howdoiverifymyaccount" class="link" role="button" aria-label="Read MoreHow do I verify my account?">
